[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    327[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # --- Triage Protocol Library (illustrative) ---
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    328[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # In production this is a Bedrock Knowledge Base index plus a
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    329[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # structured protocol-runtime that maps protocol_id to a
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    330[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # question sequence, decision logic, and care-level mapping.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    331[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Each protocol is owned by the medical director and the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    332[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # nurse-line operations leadership, reviewed before adoption,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    333[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # reviewed annually, and re-reviewed when material updates are
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    334[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # made. The protocols are versioned with effective dates; the
