[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    336[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # for any given conversation. The dict below holds one
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    337[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # illustrative chest-pain protocol with adult and pediatric
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    338[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # placeholders to demonstrate the architecture; production has
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    339[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # 40-60 protocols across the institution's nurse-line scope.
