[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1085[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1086[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Continuous emergency-screening pipeline. Detects explicit
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1087[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     emergency presentations and emergency feature
